'''Art Bug''', launched in 2001 by Jaelle Ang, an architect and artist by training, is a Singapore institution in art education. With focus on encouraging creative expression and critical thinking, Art Bug have provided art training to over 70 [[kindergarten]]s and schools in Singapore. Art Bug became a part [[Singapore Cerebral Education Group]] in 2011.<ref>http://www.artbug.com.cn</ref> Its headquarters are in Singapore and Beijing.

